{"tid":1534590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論] 機場壓力測試","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T12:10:54.000Z","uid":146119,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"87400e135201102eeec962c5a5ffa60006ed3b3f","tid":1534590,"uid":146119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:05:05.000Z","msg":"經過91既測試<br />\n大家覺得有咩要改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ec377ffe3d1ca8d13ef7711fa0122615d83c48","tid":1534590,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:05:34.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83ff93a76c0343dead636529b723c735b733d68f","tid":1534590,"uid":186640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:05:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8514db48a6fdff6d866ce5d35ab5c0c94f0182dd","tid":1534590,"uid":270327,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:07:07.000Z","msg":"主要塞馬路及黨鐵東涌線就得，因為機組人員好少搭機場快線入機場，多數搭E線車或坐東涌綫再喺嗰度搭S1/S64/S56入機場。仲有，某大航空公司嘅機組人員係好少直接喺客運大樓落巴士，而係喺 XX City 落，如果車手們不斷在附近迴旋處氹氹轉，肯定會塞爆東涌巴士入機場嘅路，仲會阻到好多本身已經住東涌嘅空姐空少及機師。<br />\n<br />\n阻旅客唔係主菜，機組人員先係。記住，堵路犯法，但塞車唔係。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c15706efca055c001c11c7c3c3c51b106a6c9595","tid":1534590,"uid":146119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:07:17.000Z","msg":"自推 10"},{"pid":"19df526e3e3be29eea9d2de084348eac0304eb8e","tid":1534590,"uid":146119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"自推 9"},{"pid":"da952395c76c5793200cb7352b50dde3e349a2dd","tid":1534590,"uid":146119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:09:34.000Z","msg":"自推 8"},{"pid":"a1f9ebb17f65305c51f8fbd87d2a430183abe641","tid":1534590,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:10:35.000Z","msg":"應該集中幫貨運做壓力測試<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6b28d3318ddd2660720db7f7ebd9ece81ff06f","tid":1534590,"uid":128117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8514db48a6fdff6d866ce5d35ab5c0c94f0182dd","tid":1534590,"uid":270327,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:07:07.000Z","msg":"主要塞馬路及黨鐵東涌線就得，因為機組人員好少搭機場快線入機場，多數搭E線車或坐東涌綫再喺嗰度搭S1/S64/S56入機場。仲有，某大航空公司嘅機組人員係好少直接喺客運大樓落巴士，而係喺 XX City 落，如果車手們不斷在附近迴旋處氹氹轉，肯定會塞爆東涌巴士入機場嘅路，仲會阻到好多本身已經住東涌嘅空姐空少及機師。<br />\n<br />\n阻旅客唔係主菜，機組人員先係。記住，堵路犯法，但塞車唔係。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:10:36.000Z","msg":"其實你一塞馬路佢地就會改搭機鐵 (or會俾公司要求佢地搭鐵)"},{"pid":"d283befa7d708a2bae169bf022393a5f0b01d916","tid":1534590,"uid":251292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:10:42.000Z","msg":"唔好黑衫 唔好帶裝（幾次都冇放tg)<br />\n拎喼拎passport"},{"pid":"a0760f69b6213068b4da51d87461dcccfbe00f9d","tid":1534590,"uid":146119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d28